Usage:
  hermes-runtime inspect run-script <path> [--url <url>] [--session <id>] [--keep-session] [--width <px>] [--height <px>] [--delay <duration>] [--timeout <duration>] [--gather <report-id>] [--compare <previous-or-bundle-path>] [--adapter <path>] [--json]

Behavior:
  Executes a project-local Node module inside the managed inspect session context.
  The module receives helpers for \`inspectAction\`, \`inspectScreenshot\`, \`gatherShow\`, \`checkpoint\`, and \`closeInspectSession\`.
