  Use \`--adapter <path>\` to override the default lookup.

Examples:
  hermes-runtime inspect run-script scripts/export-review.js --url /app/export-review
  hermes-runtime inspect run-script scripts/graft-check.js --session inspect-session-123 --keep-session
  hermes-runtime inspect run-script scripts/graft-check.js --gather latest --compare previous
  hermes-runtime inspect run-script scripts/graft-check.js --adapter .hermes/inspect-adapter.js
